(105, 'MTUwNTg2MTMwMDo5NDQ0Nzoy', 2, 0, 1, 'Daucus carota L.', 'Wild carrot', 'Apiaceae (Carrot)', NULL, NULL, '1. Native of Eurasia and a weed throughout North America (Gleason and Cronquist 1991);', NULL, NULL, 'TRUE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', '1. FOOD: gathered for food (Northeastern Oklahoma Tribal Impact: Areas related to the Tar Creek Superfund Site, 9/2/2003. Report made by the Peoria, Eastern Shawnee, Wyandotte, Seneca-Cayuga, Miami and Ottawa, listing plants commonly used by the tribes, and their lead content); 2. FOOD: roots harvested and eaten (Interview with Dani Tippman, 2005);', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'FALSE', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'TRUE', 'TRUE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'TRUE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'TRUE', NULL, 'FALSE', 'TRUE', 'FALSE', 'FALSE', 'TRUE', '2003', '2005', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-19 22:48:20', '2017-09-19 22:48:20')
